quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,43,koi jamaat apne waqt se nah agay ja sakti hai nah peechay reh sakti hai
  23,44,phir hum ne pay darpay apne paighambar bhaijtay rahay. jab kisi aُmt ke paas is ka paighambar aata tha to woh usay jutlatay they to hum bhi baaz ko baaz ke peechay ( halaak karte aur un par azaab ) laatay rahay aur un ke afsaanay banatay rahay. pas jo log imaan nahi laatay un par laanat
  23,45,phir hum ne moose aur un ke bhai Haroon ko apni nishanain aur Daleel zahir day kar bheja
  23,46,"( yani ) firaon aur is ki jamaat ki taraf, to unhon ne taqqaburkiya aur woh sarkash log they"
  23,47,kehnay lagey kekiya hum un apne jaisay do admion par imaan le ayen aur unn ko qoum ke log hamaray khidmat gaar hain
  23,48,to unn logon ne unn ki takzieeb ki so ( aakhir ) halaak kar diye gay
  23,49,aur hum ne moose ko kitaab di thi taakay woh log hadaayat payen
  23,50,"aur hum ne maryam ke betay ( eesa ) aur un ki maa ko ( apni ) nishani banaya tha aur un ko aik onche jagah par jo rehne ke Laiq thi aur jahan ( nthra howa ) pani jari tha, panah di thi"
  23,51,ay peghambroo! pakeeza cheezein khao aur amal naik karo. jo amal tum karte ho mein un se waaqif hon
  23,52,aur yeh tumhari jamaat ( haqeeqat mein ) aik hi jamaat hai aur mein tumhara perwar-digaar hon to mujh se daro
  23,53,to phir aapas mein apne kaam ko mutafarraq karkay judda judda kardiya. jo cheezein jis firqay ke paas hai woh is se khush ho raha hai
  23,54,to un ko aik muddat taq un ki ghaflat mein rehne do
  23,55,kiya yeh log khayaal karte hain ke hum jo duniya mein un ko maal aur beton se madad dete hain
  23,56,to ( is se ) un ki bhalai mein jaldi kar rahay hain ( nahi ) balkay yeh samajte hi nahi
  23,57,jo apne perwar-digaar ke khauf se drtay hain
  23,58,aur jo apne perwar-digaar ki ayaton par imaan rakhtay hain
  23,59,aur jo apne perwar-digaar ke sath shareek nahi karte
